org.metacsp.fuzzyAllenInterval

Class FuzzyAllenIntervalNetworkSolver

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.metacsp.framework.ConstraintSolver
      • org.metacsp.fuzzyAllenInterval.FuzzyAllenIntervalNetworkSolver
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class FuzzyAllenIntervalNetworkSolver
extends ConstraintSolver
    This ConstraintSolver implements a fuzzified version of Allen's path consistency algorithm, as well as search procedure to extract the optimal solution of a fuzzy temporal CSP.
    Author:
    Masoumeh Mansouri
